  "page": "Widow's Ford",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle at the Widow's Ford</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\nWidow's Ford in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a>:<br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Darry.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Darry.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/30px-House_Darry.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/45px-House_Darry.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/60px-House_Darry.svg.png 2x\" /></a><b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">House Darry</a></b></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\"><img alt=\"House Darry.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/20px-House_Darry.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/30px-House_Darry.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Darry.svg/40px-House_Darry.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Three sons of Lord Darry</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vypren\" title=\"House Vypren\"><img alt=\"House Vypren.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/20px-House_Vypren.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/30px-House_Vypren.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/40px-House_Vypren.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vorian_Vypren\" title=\"Vorian Vypren\">Vorian Vypren</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Three sons of Lord Darry †</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Hundreds</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Widow's Ford</b> is a ford in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, possibly near <a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Darry</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Widow%27s_Ford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a>, three sons of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">Darry</a> held off the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Vorian_Vypren\" title=\"Vorian Vypren\">Vorian Vypren</a> for a day and a night at the Widow's Ford. According to song, the Darrys slew hundreds before they were themselves slain.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Widow%27s_Ford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_Riverlands\" title=\"Template:Region Riv